dct_title_s: Rutgers University, Newark Campus, New Jersey 1977
dct_description_sm: Three dimensional map depicting Rutgers University, Newark campus with university buildings numbered in the building directory while local non-university buildings are lettered. Map prepared by Leslie S. Salit, Cartography Laboratory, Department of Geography, May 1977.
